    <item> 
     <title>Staff Members Recognized for Years of Service, Planned Giving</title> 
     <link>https://www.ptk.org/news/staff-years-of-service-recognized 
     <description>
      &lt;div class="field field-name-field-dateline field-type-datestamp field-label-hidden"&gt;&lt;div class="field-items"&gt;&lt;div class="field-item even"&gt;&lt;span class="date-display-single" property="dc:date" datatype="xsd:dateTime" content="2014-12-15T00:00:00-06:00"&gt;Monday, December 15, 2014&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden"&gt;&lt;div class="field-items"&gt;&lt;div class="field-item even" property="content:encoded"&gt;&lt;p&gt;Phi Theta Kappa recently recognized staff members who have reached milestone years of service with the honor society during a year-end All-Staff Meeting at the Center for Excellence.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="caption_photo right"&gt;&lt;a class="colorbox colorbox-insert-image" href="https://www.ptk.org/sites/default/files/Staff%20Service%20Awards.jpg" rel="gallery-all" title=""&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://www.ptk.org/sites/default/files/styles/medium/public/Staff%20Service%20Awards.jpg?itok=8HTs9d0u" title="" typeof="foaf:Image" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;p&gt;Headquarters staff members were recently recognized for years of service at the Center for Excellence.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Staff members recognized:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="caption_photo right"&gt;&lt;a class="colorbox colorbox-insert-image" href="https://www.ptk.org/sites/default/files/Athena%20Society.jpg" rel="gallery-all" title=""&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://www.ptk.org/sites/default/files/styles/medium/public/Athena%20Society.jpg?itok=UpcZUHNV" title="" typeof="foaf:Image" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;p&gt;The Phi Theta Kappa Foundation recently recognized Headquarters staff members who have joined the Athena Society by leaving a gift to the Foundation in their estate planning.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;15 Years:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul class="default"&gt;&lt;li&gt;Monika Byrd, Dean of Leadership Development and Service Learning&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;10 Years:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul class="default"&gt;&lt;li&gt;John Steffens, Associate Director of Application Development&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Five Years:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul class="default"&gt;&lt;li&gt;Karri Chaney, Philanthropy Coordinator&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Ron Filipowicz, Director of College Relations&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Tracy Kleven, Marketing and Communications Project Manager&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Three Years:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul class="default"&gt;&lt;li&gt;Jennifer Blalock, Chief Student Support Officer&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Brian Bostak, Shipping and Fulfillment Coordinator&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Joshua Scott Hancock, Associate Director of College Relations&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Carolyn Margoni, Associate Director of College Relations&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Steve Mulhollen, Chief Financial Officer&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Matthew Murphy, Software Engineer&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Archana Reddy, Software Engineer&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Sumati Thomas, Information Research and Data Analyst&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;In addition, the &lt;a href="http://www.ptkfoundation.org"&gt;Phi Theta Kappa Foundation&lt;/a&gt; honored those staff members who are members of the &lt;a href="http://www.ptkfoundation.org/donors/athena-legacy-society"&gt;Athena Society&lt;/a&gt;, individuals who have made the decision to leave a gift to the Foundation in their estate planning.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Athena Society members recognized:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul class="default"&gt;&lt;li&gt;Karri Chaney, Philanthropy Coordinator&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Deidra Daws, Chief of Staff&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Larry Horn, Associate Director, Information Services&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Saralyn Quinn, Senior Director, Operations &amp;amp; HR&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Mia Ramos-Shirley, Associate Director of Regional &amp;amp; Chapter Development, Division III&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Dr. Nancy Reives, Phi Theta Kappa Foundation Executive Director and CEO&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Dr. Rod Risley, Executive Director and CEO&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Reminder: The Center for Excellence will be closed December 22 through January 2, 2015, and will reopen Monday, January 5, 2015.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="field field-name-field-article-tags field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-inline clearfix"&gt;&lt;div class="field-label"&gt;Tags:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="field-items"&gt;&lt;div class="field-item even"&gt;&lt;a href="/taxonomy/term/192" typeof="skos:Concept" property="rdfs:label skos:prefLabel" datatype=""&gt;Press Room&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
