     <title>GEICO: More than Just Car Insurance</title> 
     <link>https://www.ptk.org/news/geico-partnership-feature 
     <description>
      &lt;div class="field field-name-field-dateline field-type-datestamp field-label-hidden"&gt;&lt;div class="field-items"&gt;&lt;div class="field-item even"&gt;&lt;span class="date-display-single" property="dc:date" datatype="xsd:dateTime" content="2014-10-02T00:00:00-05:00"&gt;Thursday, October 2, 2014&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden"&gt;&lt;div class="field-items"&gt;&lt;div class="field-item even" property="content:encoded"&gt;&lt;p&gt;You know its mascot, and you know its tagline. But did you know that GEICO has given more than $1 million to support scholarships and programs for Phi Theta Kappa members?&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="caption_photo right"&gt;&lt;a class="colorbox colorbox-insert-image" href="https://www.ptk.org/sites/default/files/ChrisLemaster.jpg" rel="gallery-all" title=""&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://www.ptk.org/sites/default/files/styles/medium/public/ChrisLemaster.jpg?itok=9cTkMUh2" title="" typeof="foaf:Image" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;p&gt;Chris LeMaster and the GEICO Gecko at Phi Theta Kappa&amp;#39;s 2013 Annual Convention&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Angie Goldszmidt does; she is a recipient of the 2014 GEICO Pathways to Completion Bachelor&amp;rsquo;s Degree Scholarship, which awards $1,500 each to the two top-scoring applicants for Phi Theta Kappa&amp;rsquo;s Guistwhite Scholarship.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="caption_photo right"&gt;&lt;a class="colorbox colorbox-insert-image" href="https://www.ptk.org/sites/default/files/angie%20goldszmidtweb_0.jpg" rel="gallery-all" title=""&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://www.ptk.org/sites/default/files/styles/medium/public/angie%20goldszmidtweb_0.jpg?itok=TDGp7BcX" title="" typeof="foaf:Image" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;p&gt;2014 GEICO Pathways to Completion Bachelor&amp;#39;s Degree Scholarship recipient Angie Goldszmidt&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Eight years ago, Goldszmidt was living with her family in underground shelters in Northern Israel, taking cover from Hezbollah rocket attacks. She immigrated to the United States at the age of 14. After high school, she worked 40 hours a week at a wholesale diamond company each day and as a waitress on weekends while earning a 4.0 GPA as a student at Bergen Community College in New Jersey at night.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Goldszmidt served as secretary for the Model United Nations Club and as president of her Phi Theta Kappa chapter. She hopes to earn advanced degrees in political science and become an advocate of positive change on the national and international levels.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;ldquo;Many of our students come from low-income families and broken homes, and some live in homeless shelters,&amp;rdquo; she said. &amp;ldquo;I feel it is my personal duty to do everything I can to help them graduate and support them through the transfer process.&amp;rdquo;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The partnership between GEICO and Phi Theta Kappa has proven valuable for both organizations. In addition to serving as an Annual Convention sponsor, GEICO also provides a &lt;a href="https://www.geico.com/landingpage/member-discount/?logo=17848"&gt;discount on car insurance&lt;/a&gt; to Phi Theta Kappa members and advisors. Plus, a &lt;a href="https://www.facebook.com/GEICOCareers"&gt;GEICO Career Fair&lt;/a&gt; will be hosted later in the year exclusively for Phi Theta Kappa members.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;ldquo;We value education and actively promote it within our company too,&amp;rdquo; said Deedre Daniel, GEICO&amp;rsquo;s Director, National Sales and Service: Partnership, Affinity and Membership Discounts. &amp;ldquo;It is our hope that these students go on to finish their bachelor&amp;rsquo;s degrees and find rewarding careers when they graduate.&amp;rdquo;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The GEICO Pathways to Completion Scholarship Program provides a total of $10,000 in scholarships to Phi Theta Kappa members: two awards of $1,000 at the associate level; two awards of $1,500 at the baccalaureate level; and two awards of $2,500 at the graduate level. Applications for the &lt;a href="https://www.ptk.org/become-a-member/scholarships/geico-masters"&gt;GEICO Pathway to Completion Master&amp;rsquo;s Degree Scholarship&lt;/a&gt; are now being accepted through October 31.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;ldquo;GEICO is an ideal partner, and it is fitting that their innovation would fund our first graduate-level scholarship,&amp;rdquo; said Courtney Taylor, Phi Theta Kappa&amp;rsquo;s Associate Director of Institutional Advancement. &amp;ldquo;We are thankful that they consistently go above and beyond for our members through discounts, jobs and now this scholarship program.&amp;rdquo;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The program also funds the Marshall and Mosal Leadership Awards, two awards of $5,000 each for advisors.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;ldquo;GEICO is committed to supporting Phi Theta Kappans as they pursue their education, career and lifetime goals,&amp;rdquo; said Chris LeMaster, GEICO&amp;rsquo;s Service and Event Manager: Partnership, Affinity and Membership Discounts. &amp;ldquo;We understand that for some individuals their goals may include getting an advanced degree. It is our hope that the scholarships will help alleviate some of the financial burden placed on them and allow the recipients to focus on their goals.&amp;rdquo;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;LeMaster visits with Phi Theta Kappa members and advisors regularly when he attends Nerd Nation, the Society&amp;#39;s Annual Convention. The excitement and gratitude they express for the GEICO partnership moves him every time, and he knows it&amp;rsquo;s a partnership neither organization will end anytime soon.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;ldquo;Phi Theta Kappa is one of the most passionate, energetic and driven groups that I work with,&amp;rdquo; he said. &amp;ldquo;From the staff to the members, you would be hard-pressed to find a group that lives and breathes the mission and goals of an organization as much as Phi Theta Kappa.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;ldquo;We are so fortunate to work with such a great honor society and look forward to many more years of supporting Phi Theta Kappa members and saving them money.&amp;rdquo;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="field field-name-field-article-tags field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-inline clearfix"&gt;&lt;div class="field-label"&gt;Tags:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="field-items"&gt;&lt;div class="field-item even"&gt;&lt;a href="/taxonomy/term/189" typeof="skos:Concept" property="rdfs:label skos:prefLabel" datatype=""&gt;The Experience&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
