    <item> 
     <title>NerdNation 2014 Scholarship Recipients Announced</title> 
     <link>https://www.ptk.org/news/nerd-nation-scholarships-announced 
     <description>
      &lt;div class="field field-name-field-dateline field-type-datestamp field-label-hidden"&gt;&lt;div class="field-items"&gt;&lt;div class="field-item even"&gt;&lt;span class="date-display-single" property="dc:date" datatype="xsd:dateTime" content="2014-01-23T00:00:00-06:00"&gt;Thursday, January 23, 2014&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden"&gt;&lt;div class="field-items"&gt;&lt;div class="field-item even" property="content:encoded"&gt;&lt;p&gt;Twenty chapters have received scholarship packages to attend &lt;a href="http://nerdnation.ptk.org"&gt;NerdNation 2014,&lt;/a&gt; Phi Theta Kappa&amp;rsquo;s Annual Convention, to be held April 24-26 in Orlando, Florida.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Each package is valued at $691 and will cover registration for one advisor and one chapter officer or member from each chapter to attend the Annual Convention. The scholarship also covers registration for the chapter member or officer to attend the &lt;a href="http://nerdnation.ptk.org/experience/academy"&gt;Phi Theta Kappa Academy.&lt;/a&gt; Advisors pay no fees to attend the Academy, although pre-registration is required.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Recipients of these scholarships have never attended a pre-Convention Academy or an Annual Convention.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Division I&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Alpha Rho Epsilon&lt;br /&gt;Columbus State Community College, Ohio&lt;br /&gt;Renee K. Deveaux, Advisor&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Psi Phi&lt;br /&gt;Patrick Henry Community College, Virginia&lt;br /&gt;Angela Wright, Advisor&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Alpha Kappa Lambda&lt;br /&gt;Massachusetts Bay Community College, Massachusetts&lt;br /&gt;Jill Silos-Rooney, Advisor&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Alpha Sigma Pi&lt;br /&gt;Chesapeake College, Maryland&lt;br /&gt;Jeremy Crowe, Advisor&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Alpha Xi Omicron&lt;br /&gt;Pamlico Community College, North Carolina&lt;br /&gt;Kasey Melvin, Advisor&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Division II&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Beta Iota Beta&lt;br /&gt;East Georgia State College, Georgia&lt;br /&gt;Jessica Newberry Palumbo, Advisor&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Chi Pi&lt;br /&gt;Georgia Perimeter College, Georgia&lt;br /&gt;Dr. Lauren Curtright, Advisor&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Alpha Delta Theta&lt;br /&gt;Jefferson Community &amp;amp; Technical College, Kentucky&lt;br /&gt;Linh Changaris, Advisor&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Alpha Rho Phi&lt;br /&gt;Bossier Parish Community College, Louisiana&lt;br /&gt;Michelle Triplet, Advisor&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Chi Omicron&lt;br /&gt;Jackson State Community College, Tennessee&lt;br /&gt;Donald Brown, Advisor&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Division III&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Iota Omicron&lt;br /&gt;Kaskaskia College, Illinois&lt;br /&gt;Erin Landers, Advisor&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Alpha Delta Omega&lt;br /&gt;Glen Oaks Community College, Michigan&lt;br /&gt;Ben Fries, Advisor&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Kappa Omicron&lt;br /&gt;Bismarck State College, North Dakota&lt;br /&gt;Kevin Cavanagh, Advisor&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Alpha Iota Omega&lt;br /&gt;Ellsworth Community College, Iowa&lt;br /&gt;Lisa Stock, Advisor&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Beta Nu Omicron&lt;br /&gt;Anoka Technical College, Minnesota&lt;br /&gt;Pam Prokop, Advisor&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Division IV&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Alpha Pi Xi&lt;br /&gt;Kauai Community College, Hawaii&lt;br /&gt;Ann Kennedy, Advisor&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Phi Epsilon&lt;br /&gt;Northwest College, Wyoming&lt;br /&gt;Eric Silk, Advisor&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Alpha Omega Omicron&lt;br /&gt;Kenai Peninsula College, Alaska&lt;br /&gt;Dorothy Gray, Advisor&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Alpha Pi Mu&lt;br /&gt;College of the Siskiyous, California&lt;br /&gt;Sunny Greene, Advisor&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Beta Sigma Pi&lt;br /&gt;College of Western Idaho, Idaho&lt;br /&gt;Jenica Draney, Advisor&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="field field-name-field-article-tags field-t